data.description: This handsome, traditional-style residence built by New Castle Homes is nestled on a prime corner lot within the exclusive Retreat at White Oak community in Ooltewah.  This gated enclave community offers amenities like a tennis court, clubhouse, sparkling pool, and a playful playground. The exterior of the home exudes classic elegance, inviting you in with its immaculate landscaping and a well-manicured lawn that sets the stage for the beauty within.Step inside to discover a warm and inviting atmosphere highlighted by rich hardwood flooring that seamlessly connects the open-concept living spaces. The heart of the home is adorned with a Juliet balcony, adding a touch of romance and sophistication. With ample room to entertain and relax, this home boasts four cozy bedrooms and three full, modern bathrooms, ensuring comfort for both family and guests alike.The loft area offers a flexible space that can be transformed into a media room, a play area, or a secondary family room, while the dedicated office/library space provides a tranquil retreat for work or study. The thoughtful design and attention to detail are evident throughout this home, making it a perfect fusion of functionality and style.With its sought-after location in Ooltewah, renowned for its natural beauty and convenience, this property is more than just a home--it's a lifestyle. Enjoy the serenity of your surroundings and the luxury of community amenities just steps from your door. This property promises a life of comfort and elegance, waiting for you to make it your own.
